d.</li>\n    <li> The Court phase, in which players will attempt to win the favor of powerful members of the court to aid their cause,</li>\n    <li> The Harvest phase, in which players will attempt to satisfy the demands of the Celestials while saving as many doomed souls as they can.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>At the end of the game, the player who is able to shepherd the most souls to safety, behind their player screen, will win the game.</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='text-muted'>This page does not exist. You can edit this page to create it.</span>","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"4864183","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__small/img/NRWWFpAtMhL09aPbNIvVqZh4TR8=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__micro/img/JExErQXEOov2hihB1U5f0_36JJ4=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__square/img/ixhO0mXMcPZSwS3hi9ZpaK4Aqus=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__tallthumb/img/2YOTlReA_DALQsnLFm88xZUzb9w=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__previewthumb/img/bA2vo3628EDFkI5C0BPTzjPmH6I=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__square200/img/9Wr8Usve5RrJ23rrHeFHzgIDEY4=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__original/img/AeyaIlZcjrTRRkD5vKDYTQJl-uE=/0x0/filters:format(png)/pic4864183.png"},"imagepagehref":"/image/4864183/court-of-the-dead-dark-harvest","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/9maos9R2z1BqGHY-HfqC1Q__itemrep/img/dMikX4FRsTwUpwgb_c_V23dtBQk=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic4864183.png","topimageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/o